I"„<p>Every year, the Science Olympiad Foundation (SOF) hosts the IGKO (International General Knowledge Olympiad). The IGKO Olympiad test is held for students in grades 1 to 10. Its goal is to encourage students to become more interested in current events and broaden their knowledge. Students who are participating in the IGKO Olympiad must be familiar with the IGKO Olympiad Syllabus.</p>
